<title>ạ̉nt tmlạ̉ ạlạ̉wạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tyjy trwy ạlạ̉rḍ ạlnạsẖfẗ
 tḥyy lynạ ʿẓạmnạ ạlyạbsẗ
 jysẖ ʿẓym yqwm lmjdk wtʿwḍ ạ̉yạmnạ ạlfạtrẗ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹nt tmlạ̉ ạlạ̉wạny bqwẗ rwḥk zyt wnạr
 wtʿwd wtfyḍ mn tạny sẖwqnạ rwḥk yạ jbạr
 2- ạftḥ ạlʿywn ạ̹lyh wạlknysẗ ttjml byh
 ṭạlbyn mlʾ ạlrwḥ mn tạny wạlslṭạn ạlly
 bydyh
 3- ạgẖmr ạ̉rjlnạ fy ạlzyt wạlmjd ygẖṭy lnạ
 ạlbyt
 ạʿln lynạ rw̉y̱ wạ̉ḥlạm kml fynạ yạlly bdyt
 4- sẖwqtnạ jwạnạ lhyb msẖtạqyn tạny llksyb
 ḥqq wʿdk ạlly qlth mlʾ rwḥk ạlʿjyb</lyrics>
